products.title: ASUS Cerberus GeForce GTX 1050 Ti 4GB OC Edition GDDR5 Gaming Graphics Card (Cerberus-GTX1050Ti-O4G)
features: Esports Gaming tested with major titles like League of Legends, Over watch and Player Unknown's Battlegrounds
Strong back plate support designed to reinforce circuit board
Plug and play design requires no PCIe power connectors for easy graphics upgrade
Auto-extreme Manufacturing Technology delivers premium quality and reliability with aerospace-grade Super Alloy Power II components to run faster and last longer than reference
GPU Tweak II makes monitoring performance and streaming easier than ever, featuring Game Booster and XSplit Game caster, all via an intuitive interface
products.description: Play longer and cooler than the reference to the ASUS Cerberus GTX 1050 Ti 4GB OC edition, powered by NVIDIA. GPU Tweak II enables one-click overclocking to optimize graphics performance while Auto-extreme Technology uses full machine SMT automation with aerospace-grade Super Alloy Power II components for premium quality and reliability.
